'''德瑞克·內撒尼亞爾·路克'''（{{lang-en|Derek Nathanial Luke}}，{{bd|1974年|4月24日}}）<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.foxnews.com/wires/2008Apr24/0,4670,History,00.html | work=Fox News | title=Today in History - April 24 | date=2012-05-04 | accessdate=2020-11-24 | archive-date=2015-09-24 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924180115/http://www.foxnews.com/wires/2008Apr24/0,4670,History,00.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>是一名[[美國|美國]]男演員。路克以主演[[丹佐·華盛頓|丹佐·華盛頓]]執導的《{{le|衝出逆境|Antwone Fisher (film)}}》（2002年）而聞名，首次出演電影的他為此贏得[[獨立精神獎最佳男主角|獨立精神獎最佳男主角]]<ref name="Kam">{{cite web |url=http://www.kamwilliams.com/2009/01/derek-luke-notorious-interview.html |title=Derek Luke: The Notorious Interview |accessdate=2009-06-30 |date=2009-01-25 |author=[[Kam_Williams|Kam Williams]] |publisher=KamWilliams.com |archive-date=2020-08-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200804044333/http://www.kamwilliams.com/2009/01/derek-luke-notorious-interview.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。其他著名作品如電影《[[美國隊長_(電影)|美國隊長]]》（2011年）和電視劇《[[漢娜的遺言_(電視劇)|漢娜的遺言]]》（2017年至2019年）。

== 早期生活 ==
德瑞克·路克出生於[[新泽西州|新泽西州]][[泽西市|泽西市]]，是鋼琴家瑪裘瑞·迪克森（Marjorie Dixon）和前演員莫里斯·路克（Maurice Luke）的兒子。他的父親來自[[圭亞那|圭亞那]][[乔治敦_(圭亚那)|乔治敦]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.popentertainment.com/robbinsluke.htm |title=Tim Robbins and Derek Luke interview about ''Catch a Fire'' |accessdate=2007-11-10 |year=2006 |work= |publisher=PopEntertainment.com |archive-date=2007-12-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071212010205/http://www.popentertainment.com/robbinsluke.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web| url=https://movies.yahoo.com/movie/contributor/1804502220/bio| title=Derek Luke Biography| accessdate=2007-11-10| publisher=[[Yahoo!|Yahoo!]] Movies| archive-date=2011-06-04| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110604004917/http://movies.yahoo.com/movie/contributor/1804502220/bio| dead-url=no}}</ref>。路克就讀於{{le|亨利·斯奈德高中|Henry Snyder High School}}，並從{{le|林登高中 (新澤西州)|Linden High School (New Jersey)|林登高中}}畢業<ref>Staff. [http://www.nj.com/hudson/index.ssf/2008/12/actor_derek_luke_comes_home_to.html "Actor Derek Luke comes home to talk with Snyder High students"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nj.com/hudson/index.ssf/2008/12/actor_derek_luke_comes_home_to.html |date=20181120061119 }}, ''[[The_Jersey_Journal|The Jersey Journal]]'', 2008-12-22. Accessed 2019-07-23. "Jersey City born-and-raised actor Derek Luke is at Snyder High School, where he attended, this morning to talk to students, a school official said this morning. The star of Biker Boyz, Antoine Fisher and Glory Road, is expected to talk about his life experiences and rough times growing up in Jersey City. Luke attended Snyder, but graduated from Linden High."</ref>。

